title: string_operations
text:
string_operations





Name
Description




is_palindrome
Check if a string is a palindrome.


reverse_string
Return the reversed version of the input string.


to_lowercase
Convert a string to lowercase.


to_uppercase
Convert a string to uppercase.





string_operations.is_palindrome(text)
Check if a string is a palindrome.



string_operations.reverse_string(text)
Return the reversed version of the input string.



string_operations.to_lowercase(text)
Convert a string to lowercase.



string_operations.to_uppercase(text)
Convert a string to uppercase.

title: math_operations
text:
math_operations





Name
Description




add
Return the sum of two numbers.


divide
Return the division of two numbers, handling zero division.


multiply
Return the product of two numbers.


subtract
Return the difference between two numbers.





math_operations.add(a, b)
Return the sum of two numbers.



math_operations.divide(a, b)
Return the division of two numbers, handling zero division.
